<plot>Logan and Angelique Foster are very much in love. She is an artist, he is the head of the fastest growing Fortune 500 company in history. But even though they are very happy together, Angelique often feels neglected, as if Logan loves his career, his power, his position and his wealth more than he loves her. On the night of their 10th anniversary, they have a terrible car accident. Angelique is killed, Logan is in a coma for two months. When he returns home, he begins to be haunted by the ghost of his beloved wife -- who is calling to him to join her on the other side! Will Logan hold onto his life and his possessions, or will he sacrifice everything to be with his wife? Or is there a third option???</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?025364</url></doc>
